room_title: Escape room "Doctor Madblood's Mystery Manor" by Countdown Escape Room in Virginia Beach
room_address: 5764 Princess Anne Rd Virginia Beach, VA 23462
room_description: The local late night horror show host; Dr. Madblood, has asked you over for the evening - will you accept his invite? Your party will have 60-minutes to uncover the secrets of his creepy manor and reveal his true intentions. Spine-tingling fun is surely in store for those daring enough to visit!
